plot: Shannon goes on a date with a man who she plans to invite to Vicki's engagement party. Emily helps Gina pack up her Coto house. Braunwyn and her mom Dr. Deb meet for yoga while continuing to avoid their unresolved issues. Emily is surprised at a medical diagnosis. The ladies celebrate Vicki's engagement with a "farmhouse chic" party, but Tamra melts down after seeing Kelly.
